  "id": "api/endpoints/recommendation/getRecommendationRange",
  "title": "Get Range Recommendation",
  "type": "api_endpoint",
  "category": "api",
  "content": "# Get Range Recommendation\n\nReturns a dictionary with a data property containing an array of Recommendations within a specified time range for all of the `resources` in the `resources` array that match the filter options.\n\n## Endpoint\n\n`POST /recommendations/range/get`",
  "summary": "Get Range Recommendation",
